Contact Us

Say hello on the MakerBar's <a href="http://groups.google.com/group/MakerBar">Mailing List</a> if you're interested in membership, need help on a project, have something cool to share, or want to meet the community.

You can also <a href="mailto:hello@makerbar.com">contact a MakerBar board member directly</a>. If you want to talk partnerships, academic studies, sponsorships, or marketing through the MakerBar, this is the way to go.

Swing by a <a href="http://www.meetup.com/hoboken-hackerspace">meeting</a> to see the space and meet the members. Open events are every Wednesday and Friday.

Follow <a href="http://twitter.com/makerbar">@makerbar</a> on Twitter to get project inspiration, space news, and event pictures.

Chat with us live on <a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/makerbar">#makerbar</a> on irc.freenode.net. Your mileage may vary!
